textAfterTable: Note: Backward compatible PGs are intended to be supported during the transition when you upgrade the Central Controller and PGs to the same version. Note: MR PG and Dialer must be at the same version. Note: For Outbound deployments, ES18 must be installed with UCCE 8.5(4) to work with Central Controller 9.x and 10.x.
